title: A little update
content:
Hello everyone! I publish this message to apologize for the delay in delivering the sketches; Last Monday I returned from vacation and started working on it, but due to bad luck I contracted dengue, and these last few days I have been recovering, I was able to finish 2 before that

When I feel better I will continue working on the remaining sketches and will post them all as usual

I apologize and I thank you very much for your patience.

Greetings!
